    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705580/extras/f4644ff089e37f6627b7c1a002889cf9.poster.avif?t=1761147566\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705580/extras/f4644ff089e37f6627b7c1a002889cf9.webm?t=1761147566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705580/extras/f4644ff089e37f6627b7c1a002889cf9.mp4?t=1761147566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>SiNKR 3是获奖的SiNKR极简益智游戏系列的巅峰之作。看似简单，却非常令人满足的玩法。<br><br>SiNKR 3在我们熟悉的装置(方孔和圆孔、反弹器、传送门、棘轮)上添加了新的倾斜设计，带来新的斜对角布局和台球式的物理设计。<br><br>解锁一系列的精巧装置，以下沉所有的冰球并完成每一关。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >继承自SiNKR和SiNKR 2</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>教程等级(不需要SiNKR经验)<br></li><li>高级别允许多种玩法<br></li><li>没有分数，没有计时器，没有干扰<br></li><li>响应式环境音景<br></li><li>无文本，适用于所有语言<br></li><li>迷你地图关卡选择器，挑战等级从*到***<br></li><li>多路径和可跳级</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更好的机械设计</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>对角线移动扩展游戏选项<br></li><li>弹跳的冰球注入了台球式的动态挑战<br></li><li>多步撤销有助于解决最难的关卡</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705580/extras/d73810e69e1e41b8c77fdaeb2d0d8117.poster.avif?t=1761147566\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705580/extras/d73810e69e1e41b8c77fdaeb2d0d8117.webm?t=1761147566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705580/extras/d73810e69e1e41b8c77fdaeb2d0d8117.mp4?t=1761147566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>谢谢下载，玩得开心!",
